headline: Must build out infrastructure to achieve AI dominance: Onsemi CEO
summary: Hassane El-Khoury, Onsemi CEO, says the company is still focused on the automotive industry and is making its way into AI. He speaks to Romaine Bostick and Scarlet Fu on "The Close."
